HEADWORD: Debater
<hw>De*bat"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who debates; one
given to argument; a disputant; a controvertist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Debate where leisure serves with dull <qex>debaters</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

